Kalau macam tu, biar aku teka.

540
00:43:12,010 --> 00:43:16,060
Daeng jenis tak suka menangis, simpan semua.

541
00:43:16,370 --> 00:43:19,160
Tak pernah cerita pada orang, pendam saja.

542
00:43:21,300 --> 00:43:23,131
Bodohnya. Ingat tu buat dia nampak hebat?

543
00:43:23,560 --> 00:43:26,330
Akhirnya yang sakit kau, tolol.

544
00:43:26,660 --> 00:43:29,480
Ada orang boleh kau cerita, tapi kau simpan sendiri.

545
00:43:29,590 --> 00:43:31,150
Kenapa buat-buat kuat?

546
00:43:32,830 --> 00:43:34,670
Aku kesian dekat Daeng.

547
00:43:35,300 --> 00:43:36,470
Apa masalah kau?

548
00:43:37,920 --> 00:43:39,700
P'Jo suruh aku sampaikan ni.

549
00:43:40,990 --> 00:43:42,250
Jo, kau bodoh.

550
00:43:43,210 --> 00:43:45,590
-Cakap sendiri. Aku tak nak cakap.
-Jadi?

551
00:43:45,760 --> 00:43:48,510
Ni betul-betul pasal Daeng atau orang lain?

552
00:43:51,880 --> 00:43:52,610
Daeng.

553
00:43:54,390 --> 00:43:55,600
Dia suruh aku cakap.

554
00:43:57,180 --> 00:43:58,610
Oh.

555
00:43:59,530 --> 00:44:00,580
P'Jo.

556
00:44:01,240 --> 00:44:01,580
Hmm?

557
00:44:02,020 --> 00:44:02,620
P'Thit

558
00:44:02,950 --> 00:44:06,650
