596
00:47:14,500 --> 00:47:16,310
Aku di Chicago selama tiga tahun.

597
00:47:17,140 --> 00:47:18,920
Betul kau tak nak hantar aku pergi?

598
00:47:20,180 --> 00:47:20,820
Tak.

599
