687
00:54:03,550 --> 00:54:03,940
Oh.

688
00:54:09,390 --> 00:54:12,650
Bukan senang nak kosongkan jadual untuk California.

689
00:54:13,340 --> 00:54:15,180
Aku siap suruh Direk bayarkan tiket aku.

690
00:54:16,440 --> 00:54:17,740
Kau takkan tinggalkan aku, kan?

691
00:54:24,870 --> 00:54:25,380
Hei.

692
00:54:25,930 --> 00:54:26,900
Kenapa diam je?

693
00:54:28,980 --> 00:54:30,540
Sebagai balasan aku tolong kau,

694
